{"tid":285381,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足做緊音樂治療師？","createTime":"2017-06-15T18:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T20:12:55.000Z","uid":58501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"948cf05d8704b615156add51961f5eb7a1e9d5d0","tid":285381,"uid":58501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"之前係間大型老人院見過，自己又對音樂同治療有興趣<br />\n不過google 過香港好似得十幾二十個，仲要好似冇人會請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇對呢個職業有認識既手足分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc16c132c8246508837d2772ef228135bc7dac8e","tid":285381,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢幫推"},{"pid":"d1c38d2c592423b07d0e9e572e66f8d1878b626f","tid":285381,"uid":1935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3707615a2cccad316ec868652b8032988cc80bda","tid":285381,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"呢種治療師要有專業認可資格 佢地都唔可以亂咁教無經驗既人去做一D treament唔係就會被視為unethical <br />\n利申：問讀緊expressive art therapy master既朋友得知返黎<br />\n<br />\n自己搵過相關資料希望幫到巴打你 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aal.hku.hk/tpg/programme/master-expressive-arts-therapy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aal.hku.hk%2Ftpg%2Fprogramme%2Fmaster-expressive-arts-therapy&d=Uv4d9lk%2FcCSB9o7bQzeWUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7ed296b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aal.hku.hk/tpg/programme/master-expressive-arts-therapy</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eatahk.org/training-events\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eatahk.org%2Ftraining-events&d=Uv4d9lk%2FcCSB9o7bQzeWUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ddc5b538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.eatahk.org/training-events</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cccd.hk/?a=group&amp;id=current_event&amp;doc_id=946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cccd.hk%2F%3Fa%3Dgroup%26id%3Dcurrent_event%26doc_id%3D946&d=Uv4d9lk%2FcCSB9o7bQzeWUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5e86b910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cccd.hk/?a=group&amp;id=current_event&amp;doc_id=946</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cccd.hk/uploads/cccd/201606/20160628_183356_4wrchiJKDR_f.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cccd.hk%2Fuploads%2Fcccd%2F201606%2F20160628_183356_4wrchiJKDR_f.pdf&d=Uv4d9lk%2FcCSB9o7bQzeWUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9d238a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cccd.hk/uploads/cccd/201606/20160628_183356_4wrchiJKDR_f.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"3f6e63f45c79b882792691e5ecdb7f8735b2dfce","tid":285381,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"補返 據我所知呢D master要你compulsory實習某個時數 我估計通常都return offer去返D機構 <br />\n只係識音樂治療就未必夠 所以要有幾個範疇既art therapy底先夠professional同資格出黎做治療師<br />\n（自己搵返黎既料 有錯請改）"},{"pid":"223b456bba987dedef5dbc9a3ef3db1820d4cb63","tid":285381,"uid":58501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補返 據我所知呢D master要你compulsory實習某個時數 我估計通常都return offer去返D機構 <br />\n只係識音樂治療就未必夠 所以要有幾個範疇既art therapy底先夠professional同資格出黎做治療師<br />\n（自己搵返黎既料 有錯請改）</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打幫我搵左咁多資料，巴打係咪都有興趣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以我所知音樂治療係一門專科黎<br />\n的確係要考牌，而且冇記錯得澳州同美國定英國有得考牌+讀呢個master<br />\n<br />\n但我比較想知呢個職業係香港既前景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe9c661c854db3bab4ba898db07a5adc488b167","tid":285381,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:12:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得有得諗 話哂香港好少 咁你有牌就變得搶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}